  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/CARPE-DIEM-DI-VERDI-425676664253463&quot;&gt;Carpe Diem di Verdi&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Where to stay&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Hostal CaÃ±alimeÃ±a&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;We were satisfied with this hostel. For 20 USD, we got a nice double room with a private bathroom, hot water, comfortable bed, TV and fast internet. The location is 5 minutes walking distance from the center and far from the loud bars and discos. The staff is very nice and helpful. There is a kitchen that can be used by guests.&lt;/p&gt;
